a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball VI

p.k: The Sucker / The Cage / The Rival Gumball spends all day with Bomb Kid who discovers that he may well be unprankable. / Gumball and Darwin discover that their teacher, Mr Corneille, has a secret life as a fighter. / The Watterson's look back on Anais' first days in the Watterson house. Gumball and Darwin quickly find themselves up an opponent who is able to outsmart them at every turn.
